qoutes.text: Thank you for being there whenever I need you. Thank you for always listening to my rants even though they are so annoying.
You always make me smile so easily with your goofy ahh jokes so can you please stop being so cute? I can't handle it anymore :P
My love for you grows stronger with each passing day. Thank you for being my rock and my constant source of happiness
Thank you for backing me up and supporting me in everything I do. I know I am extremely paranoid but you always make me feel safe and secure.
I am so sorry if I ever make you sad or disappoint you :( I will try to be better for you hohoho

propose.text: You have no idea how grateful I am to have you in my life. You are the reason I smile. You are the reason I laugh. I love you bei <3
